      "id": "644a6905-29b2-49c6-b746-27c3efcbc483",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The authors propose a co-training method that semi-decouples features from a single known view. With this, using the edX dataset, the authors were able to create models that predict learner behavior that were better than other alternatives. ",
